title: Clark International Airport now available for MSFS!
description:
Clark International, recently released for MSFS, boasts numerous details that enhance its comparison to the default scenery in MSFS. Known as Diosdado Macapagal International Airport from 2003 to 2014, this international airport spans parts of Angeles and Mabalacat cities within the Clark Freeport and Special Economic Zone in Pampanga province, Philippines.
